### Create a New Element [POST]

If you have discovered new element you can use this endpoint to add it

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "id": 4,
            "name": "Beryllium",
            "atomicWeight": 6.008,
            "atomicNumber": 3,
            "group": 1,
            "period": 1,
            "finder": "Luis Nicolas V ?"
        }

+ Response 204

## Manage Elements [/elements/{id}]

+ Parameters
  + id: 1

### Fetch single Element [GET]

You need one element?

